WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.720
If you find the moral-distant business of the

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:09.460
autocracy-affinent World Football Association problematic,

00:00:09.460 --> 00:00:25.340
you are in the anti-FIFA. You

00:00:24.780 --> 00:00:27.800
are then vibrating my cell phone.

00:00:28.580 --> 00:00:31.800
Of course, I immediately interrupt my

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:34.740
thoughts in the most brutal way possible to read the probably unimportant

00:00:34.740 --> 00:00:38.800
message. But then I am surprised.

00:00:40.140 --> 00:00:45.380
We have to separate, the kangaroo wrote. What?

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:50.340
I repeat eloquently. Next I get a video.

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:54.300
Känguru: You were so clear and focused and fast.

00:00:54.060 --> 00:00:55.860
Känguru: I liked that about you.

00:00:56.540 --> 00:01:01.500
But then I realized that you really write down everything I do, what I

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:05.080
look at, how long I look at it and that you read my emails.

00:01:06.060 --> 00:01:07.260
That's super creepy.

00:01:07.940 --> 00:01:10.780
You are a stalker and try to watch me completely.

00:01:10.860 --> 00:01:14.020
That doesn't feel good. And what is all this for?

00:01:14.140 --> 00:01:16.840
So you can tell others what I like and what I don't like.

00:01:17.160 --> 00:01:18.860
I don't want that anymore. We have to separate.

00:01:18.580 --> 00:01:22.860
Marc-Uwe: The kangaroo comes into the living room.

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:23.460
Känguru: Do you understand? He

00:01:23.460 --> 00:01:26.860
asks. I

00:01:26.860 --> 00:01:29.960
Känguru: say, I call the video goodbye Google.

00:01:29.340 --> 00:01:39.200
Marc-Uwe: So. I have to admit that I thought very briefly you were talking about me.

00:01:38.820 --> 00:01:40.640
Känguru: About you?

00:01:40.340 --> 00:01:44.040
Marc-Uwe: Well, because of everything, write down and then tell it.

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:56.180
But when were you clear, focused and fast? I admit.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:59.080
But what is the video supposed to be good for?

00:01:59.700 --> 00:02:05.220
The video is divided into two or in German it is called Dude. What?

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:10.780
Well, listen. The half world is becoming more and more a digital colony of the USA.

00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:15.120
And now that more than half of the Americans are celebrating the wild water slide towards

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:20.000
fascism, some wonder if that could

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.400
cause a few problems. Example dangerous,

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:28.240
Trump has sanctioned against the international criminal court.

00:02:28.580 --> 00:02:30.380
Full of the super schurken move by the way.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:36.000
And that's why Microsoft has deactivated the email account of the chief prosecutor.

00:02:36.060 --> 00:02:39.860
Also paypal, amazon, credit cards, everything is no longer possible for the affected person.

00:02:39.860 --> 00:02:45.620
Marc-Uwe: The more US tech is used, the more reprehensible the world becomes.

00:02:45.540 --> 00:02:46.280
Känguru: Exactly.

00:02:46.580 --> 00:02:50.420
Apart from the fact that, as I have already mentioned in other occasions,

00:02:50.540 --> 00:02:53.080
Big Tech, through its digital quasi-monopoly in

00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:55.800
advertising and sales interactions, is sucking massive money

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:59.160
from the real economy and is not even paying taxes seriously. But? I ask,

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:07.580
now comes hopefully a but. The kangaroo jumps on the living room table, soon

00:03:07.580 --> 00:03:11.480
the fist and calls in the finest Roland Emmerich pathos,

00:03:10.740 --> 00:03:15.480
Känguru: We will not silently spend the night,

00:03:16.040 --> 00:03:19.020
we will not pass without fighting,

00:03:19.260 --> 00:03:23.960
today we celebrate together our digital Independence Day.

00:03:25.940 --> 00:03:29.680
What? The kangaroo jumps back from

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:34.840
Känguru: the table. Every first Sunday of the month is Dit, the digital Independence Day.

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:39.220
Or in German the digital Independence Day, the DUT.

00:03:41.420 --> 00:03:43.260
Is that so? I ask, not

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.580
Känguru: yet.

00:03:44.060 --> 00:03:45.720
Marc-Uwe: The kangaroo answers,

00:03:45.500 --> 00:03:47.760
Känguru: but it could soon be so.

00:03:47.340 --> 00:03:51.680
Marc-Uwe: And what happens at Dit?

00:03:51.580 --> 00:03:57.820
Känguru: At Dit you take the time to make this change, which you have known for a long time

00:03:57.560 --> 00:04:01.860
that you could do. It was just missing to do it at the moment.

00:04:01.860 --> 00:04:07.580
So, for example, away from X to Mastodon, from WhatsApp to Signal or Threema, from Google

00:04:07.580 --> 00:04:13.220
to Ecosia or Daktaco, look in the media and sign up for Prime from Amazon

00:04:13.220 --> 00:04:17.660
for local book sales. Or if you can't get by without a big shipping dealer, then

00:04:17.660 --> 00:04:31.220
just to Otto, Konrad or any other old German brand. The goal is

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:33.400
